  "title": "Origins: MITRE ATT&CK",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Mark talk with guest Blake Strom\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/blake-strom-274122ba'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about the origins of the MITRE ATT&CK framework, how it was developed, and how it has evolved over time. We also discuss how the framework is used in the industry and its impact on cybersecurity.\n\n                  <br>\n                  We also discuss Azure Security news about Azure Monitor, Azure Application Gateway, AKS, Azure Front Door, and AMD v6 Confidential VMs.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/2584945?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2584945/\">ATT&CK</a></iframe>\n\n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/2584945/#transcript'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/azureobservabilityblog/announcing-new-public-preview-capabilities-in-azure-monitor-pipeline/4488904\">Announcing new public preview capabilities in Azure Monitor pipeline</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/web-application-firewall/ag/insights\">Azure Application Gateway Web Application Firewall (WAF) Insights (preview)</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/?id=553532\">Generally Available: Default Ruleset 2.2 in WAF for Azure Application Gateway</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/?id=557213\">Generally Available: Encryption at host & disk encryption sets support in node auto-provisioning</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/?id=556282\">Public Preview: Azure Front Door Premium now supports Azure Private Link origins in UAE North</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/?id=553966\">Generally Available: AMD v6 confidential VMs in new regions for January 2026</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/marksimos_i-am-finalizing-this-new-data-security-diagram-activity-7421543030245036032-6CFp/?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop&rcm=ACoAAAHXkxMB4EsPwQHy5XnqRPjkZK4PdOrs3Yk\">Data security diagram for the next version of the MCRA</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7432052675019657216/\">Great short video on Zero Trust</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/marksimos_i-just-posted-my-slides-from-my-talk-on-zero-activity-7423827711195787264-26eW/?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop&rcm=ACoAAAHXkxMB4EsPwQHy5XnqRPjkZK4PdOrs3Yk\">Zero Trust and AI Security</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/posts/marksimos_i-am-excited-to-talk-about-one-of-my-favorite-activity-7432820345625157633-Ucxa/?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop&rcm=ACoAAAHXkxMB4EsPwQHy5XnqRPjkZK4PdOrs3Yk\">Mark at BSid